# AI-Powered Road Safety Analytics and Accident Risk Prediction System
## Implementation Plan

Welcome to your Final Year Project! This is a comprehensive, data-driven system integrating Machine Learning, Computer Vision, Backend API development, and Frontend Data Visualization. 

This project is perfectly sized for a 2-3 month timeline and will look highly impressive to your evaluators.

